Package CDArchiveProject

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ArchiveConsole  
    AutomationConsole
    The AutomationConsole class is meant to control a robot to manipulate a physical collection of CDs.
    CDRecord
    The CDRecord class is used to store data corresponding to a specific CD.
    CDRecordTableModel
    The CDRecordTableModel class provides a tableModel format that allows CDRecord data to be stored in a table.
    ErrorWindow
    The ErrorWindow class is a simple popup window that can be called by the main application.
    RecordStorage
    The RecordStorage class contains 2 methods used to read and write the CDRecords to a file.
